::: {.callout-important}
## Important Note About Scheduling

Due to limited practical evaluation time slots, we strongly encourage candidates to select the earliest available interview times. Early scheduling helps ensure:

- Quicker progression to the practical evaluation phase
- Better availability of evaluation slots
- Faster overall application process
- More flexibility in scheduling your practical evaluation

*Selecting an early interview slot significantly improves your chances of securing a preferred practical evaluation time.*
:::
:::

## Final Assessment {.unnumbered}

### Session Availability

Currently, practical evaluation sessions are only available on:

- Limited single sessions on Thursdays
- Limited single sessions on Fridays

*Please plan accordingly when considering your application timeline and availability.*

::: {.callout-note}
## Professional Skills Assessment

Selected candidates will be invited to participate in a hands-on evaluation day to:

- Experience our practice culture firsthand
- Demonstrate clinical skills in a real healthcare setting
- Interact with our team and patients
- Showcase your expertise in action

This professional development opportunity:

- Provides real-world clinical experience
- Offers valuable mentorship and feedback
- Helps assess team compatibility
- Is offered as a voluntary evaluation session
- Functions as an unpaid learning experience

*This practical assessment is a standard part of our evaluation process, allowing both parties to ensure an ideal fit.*
:::

